{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616740/extras/HeaderGif_2.gif?t=1731519600\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Handsome and Brave is a story about a <strong>World</strong> in turmoil and a <strong>Knight</strong> that can't save it. But he's not alone, he has you. As a <strong>Watcher</strong> you can pickup, move, and most importantly throw the <strong><i>ragdoll</i></strong>\u00a0<strong>Knight</strong>. Together you'll embark on an epic adventure to vanquish the evil <strong>Wizard</strong> and restore <strong>Law</strong> to the <strong>World</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Solving Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The <strong>Knight's</strong> uniquely resistant body and can-do attitude make him the perfect tool for any occasion. Some of his uses are:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Breaking Rocks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Opening Locks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Baking Bread</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Turning Cranks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Switching Switches</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Farming Produce</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Vanquishing villains</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Producing lasting pieces of art</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And much more!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It's up to you to utilize his <strong><i>ragdoll</i></strong> body to explore this beautiful broken <strong>World</strong> at your own pace and solve the clever puzzles left by the dastardly people that broke it.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Helping People</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2616740/extras/CharacterGif.gif?t=1731519600\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Along the way you'll meet an ambitious Director, distraught Villagers, and misguided gods. All of them have 